      "date": "2012-07-25 13:28:45.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.2/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/7fb96eb4-d653-11e1-bde4-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
