          "date": "2012-07-25 05:20:06.000000000",
          "tz": 480
        },
        "subject": "LU-220 open: try open_by_fid for the known object",
        "message": "LU-220 open: try open_by_fid for the known object\n\nIf the current path for thread1 on client1 is renamed by thread2\non client2, then when thread1 tries to open its current path, it\nshould use the fid, but not the name. Otherwise, the open on MDS\nwill hit unexpected \"-ENOENT\".\n\nSigned-off-by: Fan Yong <yong.fan@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I905113167ebd6fe5f0185007d0e9c77083342680\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
